name: Furniture_of_America_Zarina_Walnut_6-shelf_Wall-mounted_Bathroom_Tower_Cabinet
reviews: We ordered two for our newly remodeled bathroom, and love them! lots of extra storage space!!!!
I tookout my closet in the bathroom to minimize to this. It appears it will work fine.

You put this together yourself...it isnt hard with help if you're construction challenged. It is heavy because its partical board covered in a walnut colored skin. Its sturdy and holding lots of hair hoo hoos and product.
Modern storage cabinet was perfect for our bathroom.
Way too expensive for something that looks so cheap. And it's so much to pack it up and send it back.. Very disappointed..
description:
Instantly create storage space in any room with this transitional tower cabinet. Featuring six shelves, two metal support legs and a wall-mounted feature, this metal cabinet subtly provides additional space for linens and other household items while seamlessly blending into natural and modern decor schemes with its elegant walnut finish.
